## SOURCE CODE:
```
import java.util.*;
public class Main{
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n=sc.nextInt();
        int[] a=new int[n];
        double sum=0;
        for(int i=0;i<n;i++){
            a[i]=sc.nextInt();
            sum+=a[i];
        }
        double avg=sum/n;
        System.out.printf("The average of elements is %.2f",avg);
    }
}
```

